"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reflow Paragraph</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> -- Cause all the lines in the paragraph the cursor "
"is in to be wrapped to the specified outgoing mail wrap column."
msgstr ""

